cast.overview: Found inside a shining stalk of bamboo by an old bamboo cutter and his wife, a tiny girl grows rapidly into an exquisite young lady. The mysterious young princess enthrals all who encounter her. But, ultimately, she must confront her fate.
cast.title: The Tale of The Princess Kaguya

also_known_as: たてかわ しのすけ
details.biography: Shinosuke Tatekawa (立川 志の輔, Tatekawa Shinosuke, February 15, 1954) is a Japanese rakugo performer, talent, and moderator. His real name is Teruo Takeuchi (竹内 照雄, Takeuchi Teruo). He is from Shinminato City, Toyama Prefecture (currently Imizu City). He is affiliated with Shinofisu (㈱シノフィス所).
details.name: Shinosuke Tatekawa
